      <title>乌克兰盟友淡化泽连斯基“胜利计划”取得突破的希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/ukraine-s-allies-play-down-hopes-for-zelenskiy-s-victory-plan-breakthrough</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西方官员试图降低人们对乌克兰总统泽连斯基本周在纽约提出的结束战争计划的期望，称他们认为该计划不会为与俄罗斯的冲突带来突破。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/ukraine-s-allies-play-down-hopes-for-zelenskiy-s-victory-plan-breakthrough</guid>
